title: Adventure Time [iTunes, 1080p HD] volumes 1 to 5
description:
Adventure Time Volumes 1 to 5

Source: iTunes, 1080p HD downloads

These are the original streams from iTunes, they have not been transcoded. The
only higher quality achievable would be from a Bluray rip. I just decrypted /
removed the DRM, scrubbed the metadata of confidential information, and for your
convenience added chapter markers to separate intros, credits, and individual
episodes within the files. Note that on iTunes, season 5 is split in half since
it's twice as long as the other seasons. They call them volume 5 and volume 6.
So this torrent only has half of season 5. The rest isn't complete yet.

Also note that the full season uploads by "DeLtA_Sn1p3r" are NOT 1080p. They're
shitty upscales. As far as I know, these are the only 1080p full seasons on TPB.
